author: AFP
title: Thousands flock to leave Wuhan as outbound travel ban ends
description: Crowds of passengers filed into the city's Wuchang station to catch the first trains set to pull out of the city of 11 million shortly after midnight.
content:
WUHAN: Thousands of travellers flocked to catch trains leaving 
Wuhan early Wednesday as authorities lifted a more than two-month ban on outbound travel from the hard-hit Chinese city where the global coronavirus pandemic first emerged.
